item.title: ENVX
item.description: score:37 Chances: Enovix achieves quarterly milestone by producing 18,000 cells. Positive response to Enovix’s high-volume production facility location in Malaysia. Multiple leadership additions and appointments to the board of directors. Successful UL1642 safety certification for Enovix’s wearable cells. Participation in investor conferences to connect with potential investors.
